PART 5: FIBONACCI 2-3 DECOMPOSITION
======================================================================

  Fibonacci sequence mod 4 (period 6):
  [1, 1, 2, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1, 2, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1, 2, 3, 1, 0, 1, 1, 2, 3]

  Fibonacci numbers decomposed into 2s and 3s:
    F(1) =     1: 0 compositions into (2,3)
    F(2) =     1: 0 compositions into (2,3)
    F(3) =     2: 1 compositions into (2,3)
    F(4) =     3: 1 compositions into (2,3)
    F(5) =     5: 2 compositions into (2,3)
    F(6) =     8: 4 compositions into (2,3)
    F(7) =    13: 16 compositions into (2,3)
